for all of the following tags: p,h1-h6,italic,strong,code, their behavior should be {
  if i have strong:this is a paragraph, it will mean **this is a paragraph**
  with strong:, we will "promote" the strong effect "all the way to the end of the current line"
  in order to control which words should be marked as strong, we use strong{...} to group them
  for example:
  this is a strong{very important} message
  please make sure the tutorial also reflect the logic mentioned above
}
